{"tid":782384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警掃黃雞竇放生兩名休班警  ICAC拉4警","createTime":"2018-08-16T16:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T15:25:01.000Z","uid":5195,"like":640,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"8766e7a7e77ebbf0836ea5ccc36282c6b2572cb8","tid":782384,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"消息稱，廉政公署周四(16日)中午在深水埗警署及旺角警署調查後，帶走約4名警務人員，包括現役軍裝警員及特別職務隊員人員，職級由警員至警長，其中一人是女警；而廉署今次行動，緣於日前警方一次掃黃行動中，在一個賣淫場所遇上兩名休班警員，當警方在場調查期間，有人開後門讓休班警員離去。事後有人向廉署舉報，廉署人員調查後，昨到警署帶走相關人士協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180817/58572977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58572977&d=vXIrtQr4zSkx1uc2bfDxFwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=fed50a1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58572977&h=1da66fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180817/58572977</a>"},{"pid":"38bd962c5f0746604e97852b5a1470ad4247b759","tid":782384,"uid":32577,"like":377,"dislike":7,"score":370,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:50:33.000Z","msg":"呀蛇叫雞唔洗你教！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679d2897ebc0a7b4aecfc24f7c070f8865028e45","tid":782384,"uid":123587,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"WHY NEED TO RUN AWAY?"},{"pid":"bdcf65d14f98cfd2ea306b7407097b89b0adb5f6","tid":782384,"uid":35930,"like":220,"dislike":1,"score":219,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"休班警叫雞犯法咩？"},{"pid":"576e1a26241ec5103635f454c6b2ecd1443dd07a","tid":782384,"uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"玩3p?"},{"pid":"21ab51d98ec0b84b430a52228910b327cb2f0b42","tid":782384,"uid":6222,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":0,"reply